'''蘇斯瓦族'''（Secwépemc，{{lang-en|Shuswap people}}），是一支分布於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[英屬哥倫比亞|英屬哥倫比亞]]的[[第一民族|第一民族]]，其族國領土面積約145,000平方公里。<ref name="census">{{Cite web |url=http://www12.statcan.ca/english/census06/data/topics/RetrieveProductTable.cfm?ALEVEL=3&APATH=3&CATNO=&DETAIL=0&DIM=&DS=99&FL=0&FREE=0&GAL=0&GC=99&GK=NA&GRP=1&IPS=&METH=0&ORDER=1&PID=89189&PTYPE=88971&RL=0&S=1&ShowAll=No&StartRow=1&SUB=705&Temporal=2006&Theme=70&VID=0&VNAMEE=&VNAMEF= |title=Statistics Canada: 2006 Census |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2013-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016163022/http://www12.statcan.ca/english/census06/data/topics/RetrieveProductTable.cfm?ALEVEL=3&APATH=3&CATNO=&DETAIL=0&DIM=&DS=99&FL=0&FREE=0&GAL=0&GC=99&GK=NA&GRP=1&IPS=&METH=0&ORDER=1&PID=89189&PTYPE=88971&RL=0&S=1&ShowAll=No&StartRow=1&SUB=705&Temporal=2006&Theme=70&VID=0&VNAMEE=&VNAMEF= |dead-url=no }}</ref>

蘇斯瓦族傳統上以漁獵、貿易維生，其傳統語言{{tsl|en|Shuswap language|蘇斯瓦語}}屬於[[薩利希語系|薩利希語系]]，語言使用者約1600人。當前族人正與學界合作，努力復振蘇斯瓦的語言，文化與傳統。

除成立族國，蘇斯瓦族亦積極參與社運，成立政治、教育機構，如蘇斯瓦族國理事會、蘇斯瓦文化教育協會等。<ref name=" Handbook">{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.hr/books?id=SUEqUylPDJEC&pg=PA205&lpg=PA205&dq=Shuswap+Lake+Division&source=bl&ots=1WQs1kQSNj&sig=QNHqHhQSHgsLqqKCy4VZ7Mgv00g&hl=en&ei=QruMTMj2J8TDswaZ0a3TAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Shuswap%20Lake%20Division&f=false |title=Handbook of North American Indians, V. 12, Plateau, Opseg 5 |access-date=2021-01-29 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208170527/https://books.google.hr/books?id=SUEqUylPDJEC&pg=PA205&lpg=PA205&dq=Shuswap+Lake+Division&source=bl&ots=1WQs1kQSNj&sig=QNHqHhQSHgsLqqKCy4VZ7Mgv00g&hl=en&ei=QruMTMj2J8TDswaZ0a3TAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Shuswap%20Lake%20Division&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>

